data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Key Largo! This charming single-family residence boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. Situated on an oversized corner lot, the property offers a paved driveway and is surrounded by lush landscaping.  From the front door, you'll walk into the LARGE living area, flowing through to the kitchen and Florida room, great for home office, or workout space.The kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. The sleek and modern design seamlessly flows into the living spaces.  Location is key, and this residence excels in that department. Just one block from the marina, you'll have easy access to for boating and water activities.  Downtown Key Largo and Key Largo Park are within walking distance, ensuring that shopping, dining, and recreation are always just a short stroll away. Close to schools & only hour to Miami Airport.
